sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant B as Browser (UaClient)
    participant RT as ServerRuntime
    participant S as ServerSession
    participant SUB as ServerSubscription
    participant MI as MonitoredItemService
    participant AS as Address space

    Note over B,SUB: Implemented in common today: full Phase 1 message codec,<br/>decoded-request routing in ServerRuntime,<br/>live-session orchestration in ServerSession,<br/>and per-subscription runtime for queueing, publish-interval gating,<br/>keep-alives, acknowledgements, and replay

    B->>RT: CreateSubscriptionRequest<br/>(requestHandle, publishingInterval, keepAlive)
    RT->>S: decoded request envelope
    S->>SUB: create subscription (id=N)
    RT-->>B: CreateSubscriptionResponse (id=N)

    B->>RT: CreateMonitoredItemsRequest<br/>(requestHandle, subId=N, NodeId[], samplingInterval)
    RT->>S: decoded request envelope
    S->>MI: CreateMonitoredItems
    MI->>AS: attach adapter per item
    AS-->>MI: initial DataValue[]
    MI-->>SUB: queue initial values
    MI-->>S: monitoredItemId[]
    RT-->>B: CreateMonitoredItemsResponse

    B->>RT: ModifySubscription / SetPublishingMode / SetMonitoringMode
    RT->>S: decoded request envelope
    RT-->>B: matching response envelopes
    B->>RT: ModifyMonitoredItems / DeleteMonitoredItems / DeleteSubscriptions
    RT->>S: decoded request envelope
    RT-->>B: matching response envelopes

    Note over B,RT: Beast transport / TLS / origin checks wrap this common runtime.<br/>The runtime now parks PublishRequest handlers until a deadline fires.

    loop Publish pump
        B->>RT: PublishRequest (requestHandle, acks for prior seq)
        RT->>S: apply acknowledgements + poll publish state
        alt notification already due
            S->>SUB: drain next ready notification
            SUB-->>S: NotificationMessage (changes)
            RT-->>B: PublishResponse (seq, notifications)
        else nothing due yet
            S-->>RT: next publish deadline
            RT->>RT: park request on executor until deadline
            alt publishing interval elapsed with queued data
                RT->>S: poll publish state again
                S->>SUB: drain queued notification
                SUB-->>S: NotificationMessage (changes)
                RT-->>B: PublishResponse (seq, notifications)
            else keep-alive due after MaxKeepAliveCount cycles
                RT->>S: poll publish state again
                S->>SUB: emit empty keep-alive
                RT-->>B: PublishResponse (keep-alive, no notifications)
            end
        end
    end

    Note over B,RT: Connection drops, browser reconnects

    B->>RT: TransferSubscriptionsRequest(requestHandle, subId=N)
    RT->>S: decoded request envelope
    alt session still alive
        RT-->>B: Good, subscription transferred
    else session expired
        RT-->>B: BadSessionIdInvalid
        B->>RT: CreateSubscription + CreateMonitoredItems (resume)
    end

    B->>RT: RepublishRequest(requestHandle, subId=N, seq=last_acked+1)
    RT->>S: decoded request envelope
    RT-->>B: PublishResponse (replayed)
